headline: 3 Reasons We’re Fans of AutoZone (AZO)
summary: Since August 2020, the S&P 500 has delivered a total return of 90.8%. But one standout stock has more than doubled the market - over the past five years, AutoZone has surged 237% to $4,001 per share. Its momentum hasn’t stopped as it’s also gained 15.3% in the last six months, beating the S&P by 9.9%.
